{"id":"8808c38f-12f4-4254-8c08-595b3b491099","name":"Reed Richards","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\"When the mice stop dying, the Fantastic Four will return.\"<img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/8_Jfc88YEbRk74FV3wMpJ.webp\" style=\"width: 284.5px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Anthony_Stark_(Earth-6160)\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>\"You</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em> propose we re-create this other world </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Earth-6160\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>here</em></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>?</em></strong><em> This... </em><strong><em>\"</em></strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Earth-616\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 0, 255);\"><strong><em>Earth Six-One-Six</em></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>\"?</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/DFcLaP5r4W5YjmP-CAa_N.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In an untampered version of Earth 6160's history, the exposure to the </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Glossary:Cosmic_Radiation\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">cosmic ray</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> storm would have caused Reed and Sue Storm, Ben Grimm and Johnny Storm to develop super-powers, becoming the super hero team and family known as the </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mw-disambig\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Fantastic_Four\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Fantastic Four</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">. However, Reed's reality had secretly been invaded by the </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Reed_Richards_(Earth-1610)\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Maker</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, a villainous alternate version of Reed himself, who had set out to reshape a world to his image.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/m9c4SBxbKKY4jrGvuGXQG.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The Maker altered history to his whims, veering the world off its intended course. As part of his plan, the Maker delayed Reed's fateful space flight by hours by altering Reed's calculations, which delayed the flight by several hours and caused the crew to miss the cosmic storm.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/9RWBkdJFU1jH80WQ6Ur3d.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Following Reed's life collapsing, the Maker further toyed with Reed by abducting and imprisoning him within '</span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Dome\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The City'</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, his base of operations in </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Latveria\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Latveria</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">. Using the temporally accelerated environment of the City, The Maker repeatedly tortured Reed, surgically disfiguring him and goading him into accepting that his name was <strong>Doom</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Claiming that he doomed his loved ones and that he should just","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"j_9BsmO21ydiBBygye_y3.webp","creator":"The TiredTimes","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🦸 Hero","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":71,"messages":754,"created_at":"2026-01-25T09:37:15.838560+00:00"}